%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 01c2cf2a4b2c62142a7668242814b230, type: 3}
  m_Name: TextConfig.Dialogs
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  category: Dialogs
  textDataList:
  - id: node_0001_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Wow, so this is the legendary Star Academy. Starting today, this is
        where I\u2019m going to shine."
    - language: 1
      text: "Wow, \u0111\xE2y ch\xEDnh l\xE0 H\u1ECDc Vi\u1EC7n Ng\xF4i Sao trong
        truy\u1EC1n thuy\u1EBFt sao. T\u1EEB ng\xE0y h\xF4m nay \u0111\xE2y s\u1EBD
        l\xE0 n\u01A1i m\xECnh \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\u1ECFa s\xE1ng."
  - id: node_0001_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Hey, I heard that guy is the Headmaster's son, right?
    - language: 1
      text: "\xCA, nghe n\xF3i th\u1EB1ng kia l\xE0 con l\xE3o hi\u1EC7u tr\u01B0\u1EDFng
        ph\u1EA3i kh\xF4ng."
  - id: node_0001_0003
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Yeah, that's him. Just another privileged daddy's boy. (Sighs) I highly
        doubt he can actually do anything useful.
    - language: 1
      text: "\u1EEA, l\xE0 n\xF3 \u0111\xF3, l\u1EA1i th\xEAm m\u1ED9t th\u1EB1ng
        con \xF4ng ch\xE1u cha. Haizz, kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt c\xF3 l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
        tr\xF2 tr\u1ED1ng g\xEC kh\xF4ng n\u1EEFa."
  - id: node_0001_0004
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Definitely not. These rich kids just coast by on their family connections.
    - language: 1
      text: "Ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn l\xE0 kh\xF4ng r\u1ED3i, m\u1EA5y th\u1EB1ng c\xF3
        ti\u1EC1n m\xE0, to\xE0n d\u1EF1a v\xE0o quy\u1EC1n th\u1EBF."
  - id: node_0001_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: (Thinking back to last night's conversation...) ---
    - language: 1
      text: "(H\u1ED3i t\u01B0\u1EDFng l\u1EA1i cu\u1ED9c tr\xF2 chuy\u1EC7n t\u1ED1i
        h\xF4m qua...) ---"
  - id: node_0001_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: In the next few days, I will secure a position for you at the academy,
        and give you the best spirit beasts.
    - language: 1
      text: "M\u1EA5y h\xF4m n\u1EEFa, ta s\u1EBD s\u1EAFp \u0111\u1EB7t cho con
        m\u1ED9t v\u1ECB tr\xED t\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n, cho con nh\u1EEFng linh
        th\xFA gi\u1ECFi nh\u1EA5t."
  - id: node_0001_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: All you have to do is perform well and climb the ranks.
    - language: 1
      text: "Vi\u1EC7c con c\u1EA7n l\xE0m ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n th\u1EADt
        t\u1ED1t \u0111\u1EC3 th\u0103ng ti\u1EBFn th\xF4i."
  - id: node_0001_0008
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: I don't need all that. I appreciate you helping me become a coach at
        the academy.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy, con c\u1EA3m \u01A1n b\u1ED1
        \u0111\xE3 gi\xFAp con \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n
        vi\xEAn t\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n"
  - id: node_0001_0009
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: But as for the rest... I'm going to have to decline.
    - language: 1
      text: "Nh\u01B0ng nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u c\xF2n l\u1EA1i \u2026 con xin
        ph\xE9p t\u1EEB ch\u1ED1i."
  - id: node_0001_0010
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: You are my son. Everything has been arranged, do not try to defy me.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con l\xE0 con trai c\u1EE7a ta, t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 m\u1ECDi th\u1EE9 ta
        \u0111\xE3 chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB r\u1ED3i, \u0111\u1EEBng c\u1ED1 c\xE3i l\u1EDDi
        ta."
  - id: node_0001_0011
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: But like I said, I work by my own principles. I refuse to leave any student
        behind, and I don't want to just be known as your son.
    - language: 1
      text: "Nh\u01B0ng con c\u0169ng \u0111\xE3 n\xF3i r\u1ED3i, con l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c
        theo t\xF4n ch\u1EC9 c\u1EE7a m\xECnh, con kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n b\u1ECF b\u1EA5t
        c\u1EE9 h\u1ECDc vi\xEAn n\xE0o \u1EDF l\u1EA1i c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng
        mu\u1ED1n ph\u1EA3i mang c\xE1i danh con c\u1EE7a cha."
  - id: node_0001_0012
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: That much is obvious. Eventually, you will understand what I mean...
    - language: 1
      text: "V\u1ED1n d\u0129 \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0111\xF3 l\xE0 hi\u1EC3n nhi\xEAn,
        r\u1ED3i con s\u1EBD hi\u1EC3u nh\u1EEFng g\xEC ta n\xF3i\u2026"
